Class Summary
Slot Graphics panel to plot several traces in the same time and values coordinate axis on a single panel.
ColorModeBW Black and white color mode, all traces drawn in black.
ColorModeBySegment Color mode to color traces by segment, color changes at gaps
ColorModeBySource Color mode to color traces by source, color changes at sources boundaries
CommentDialog Dialog to add comments during HTML report generation.
DefaultSlotFactory Default channel view factory, generates ordinary Slot
FileChooser Customized file chooser to select files handled by TraceView
GraphPanel This is graphics container; it contains a list of Slot(s) (panels) and renders them as a 1-column table; responsible for Slot selecting and ordering selecting time and values ranges, holds information about current representation state.
GraphUtil Sets of general procedures used for gui construction
MeanModeDisabled State pattern realization for mean mode, meaning disabled
MeanModeEnabled State pattern realization for mean mode, meaning enabled
OffsetModeDisabled State pattern realization for offset mode, offset disabled
OffsetModeEnabled State pattern realization for offset mode, offset enabled

ScaleModeAuto State pattern realization for scale mode, AUTO scaling.
ScaleModeCom State pattern realization for scale mode, COM scaling.
ScaleModeXhair State pattern realization for scale mode, XHAIR scaling.
